[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "In this time forty buildings, counting small and large, have been built, and all except four are almost wholly the product of student labour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "Not a few times, when a new student has been led into the temptation of marring the looks of some building by leadpencil marks or by the cuts of a jack knife, I have heard an old student remind him: \"Don't do that. That is our building.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "I had always sympathized with the \"Children of Israel,\" in their task of \"making bricks without straw,\" but ours was the task of making bricks with no money and no experience.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "In the first place, the work was hard and dirty, and it was difficult to get the students to help.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "When it came to brickmaking, their distaste for manual labour in connection with book education became especially manifest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "We tried several locations before we opened up a pit that furnished brick clay.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "After a good deal of effort we moulded about twenty five thousand bricks, and put them into a kiln to be burned.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "This kiln turned out to be a failure, because it was not properly constructed or properly burned.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "We began at once, however, on a second kiln.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "Several of the teachers, however, who had been trained in the industries at Hampton, volunteered their services, and in some way we succeeded in getting a third kiln ready for burning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "The burning of a kiln required about a week.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000010_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000010_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "For the third time we had failed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "As the people of the neighbourhood came to us to buy bricks, we got acquainted with them; they traded with us and we with them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "Our business interests became intermingled.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "We had something which they wanted; they had something which we wanted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000013_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000013_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "This, in a large measure, helped to lay the foundation for the pleasant relations that have continued to exist between us and the white people in that section, and which now extend throughout the South.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "Wherever one of our brickmakers has gone in the South, we find that he has something to contribute to the well-being of the community into which he has gone; something that has made the community feel that, in a degree, it is indebted to him, and perhaps, to a certain extent, dependent upon him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "In this way pleasant relations between the races have been simulated.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "My experience is that there is something in human nature which always makes an individual recognize and reward merit, no matter under what colour of skin merit is found.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "I have found, too, that it is the visible, the tangible, that goes a long ways in softening prejudices. The actual sight of a first-class house that a Negro has built is ten times more potent than pages of discussion about a house that he ought to build, or perhaps could build.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "Early one morning I was standing near the dining room door listening to the complaints of the students.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "The complaints that morning were especially emphatic and numerous, because the whole breakfast had been a failure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3271_169289_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3271/169289/3271_169289_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3271",
        "content": "When she reached the well, she found that the rope was broken and that she could get no water.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]